title: Corowa Cougars
text:
Corowa Cougars Rugby League Football Club is an Australian <a href="rugby%20league">rugby league</a> football club based on the New South Wales and Victorian border. The club is based at <a href="Corowa%2C%20New%20South%20Wales">Corowa, New South Wales</a> formed in the late 1987. They conduct teams for both junior and senior teams.
